ITALY
---------
Date: Fri, 07 Jan 2000 17:04:28 +0000
From: Urbano <pasquale.urbano@unifi.it>

The most comprehensive epidemiological information in Italy is managed by
the Istituto Superiore di Sanita. A good link is:
http://simi3.iss.it/malattie.html
[Better yet is:
http://simi3.iss.it/SIMInews.html
Quarterly report on infectious diseases, in Italian, Adobe Acrobat files.
Latest available is July 1999 issue  Mod.JW]
