UNITED KINGDOM (Correction)
-----------------------------
Date: Thu, 6 Jan 2000 15:19:15 -0000
From: John.Bremner@csuh.nhs.uk

CDR Weekly data
http://www.phls.co.uk/publications/cdr.htm
are for England & Wales only (not the whole UK) unless otherwise stated.
Scotland is covered by SCIEH Weekly Report (Scottish Centre for Infection
and Environmental Health, Clifton House, Clifton Place, Glasgow G3 7LN,
Scotland. Phone +44-141-300-1100. Fax +44-141-300-1172
[SCIEH has a website,
http://www.show.scot.nhs.uk/scieh/index.htm
that says:
>expanded content, including data tables for a range of infectious diseases
and
environmental hazards, will be available at the beginning of October 1999<
but we couldn´t find any  Mod.JW]
